This tool extracts API documentation from source code JSDoc comments and generates markdown files.

### Features

- Parses JSDoc comments from source files
- Supports multiple file types (e.g., `.js`, `.ts`)
- Outputs documentation in markdown format
- Plugin support for custom processing

---

## Example Plugin Template

```js
// example-plugin.js
