  process(doc) {
    // Modify the doc object as needed
    doc.description = doc.description.toUpperCase();
    return doc;
  }
};
```

---

## Configuration Example

```json
{
  "input": "./src",
  "output": "./docs/api.md",
  "fileExtensions": [".js", ".ts"],
  "plugins": [
    "./example-plugin.js"
  ]
}
```

---

## Usage

1. Install dependencies.
2. Configure the generator with the above config.
3. Run the generator to produce markdown documentation.

